From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: OnePlus13 KernelBuilder <noreply@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0700
Subject: [PATCH] net: integrate BBRv3 with locked OnePlus Android 15 6.6

Rebase the integration portion of the pinned WildKernels BBRv3 backport
without semantic changes onto the locked OnePlus 6.6 source. The BBRv3
implementation itself is copied separately from the same pinned source patch
as a reviewable GPL/BSD source file.

Upstream-patch: WildKernels/kernel_patches@2ee34500cb4c3ee954ba36090e11f6ff08b3ec2f
Upstream-file: common/bbrv3/0001-net-tcp-backport-BBRv3-to-android15-6.6.patch
Rebased-on: OnePlusOSS/android_kernel_common_oneplus_sm8750@9920459dfb0080dd8a81c41d95701483857f804a

